text: R端f端s Du Sol is a electronic music group from Sydney, Australia. The bands members are Tyrone Lindquist, John George and James Hunt. Their first album is called Atlas which reached number one in Australia. The band formed in 2010, where the three met at a jam session in Byron Bay, New South Wales.
